Class RelationModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.output.relation.RelationModel

  • public class RelationModel
extends Object
    This class models relation with some additional assumptions: 1. items in the header can have the same name; 2. each item within the tuple can have several values.

    Ruslan Fayzrakhmanov 31 Jan 2017
